Response body data format:
A JSON object holding data about a single movie, containing an ID, title, and classes property. Example:
{    
    id: 1,
    title: 'Pokemon the Movie',
    clases: {
      description: 'An animated movie',
      genre: 'Animated',
      director: 'Nintendo',
      image_URL: 'http://www.test.com',
      featured: 'true/false'
      }
    },

